{"tid":1325351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Time: 香港示威當選互聯網25大具影響力人物","createTime":"2019-07-17T00:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T01:30:46.000Z","uid":45975,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc078c55177722fe2a10eaf064574951b938383b","tid":1325351,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"美國《時代雜誌》公布互聯網25大具影響力人物，香港示威者榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n《時代雜誌》說，在反修例示威活動中，無單一領導者，示威者使用網上討論區「連登」及通訊軟件「Telegram」決定行動，包括遊行至外國領事館，以及包圍警察總部。文章引述一位Telegram示威頻道的管理員形容，過程是「直接民主」。<br />\n<br />\n《時代雜誌》又說，網民在討論區令示威行動的帖文引起關注，Telegram的投票及聊天室功能，令示威者迅速動員或改變策略，而示威活動提示、法律援助資訊、諮詢及情緒支援，都是透過網上進行。 <br />\n<br />\n除了香港示威者，上榜的亦包括美國總統特朗普、英國哈里王子與夫人梅根等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468773-20190717.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468773-20190717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=4f75c085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468773-20190717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1b247635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468773-20190717.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n大家準備好戒嚴未？<br />\n係戒嚴區見到皇軍要敬禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係可以一槍打死你。"},{"pid":"0cecd72c531209fd6e8d9ca0496b3e87a31e8b7f","tid":1325351,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:49:22.000Z","msg":"又關連登事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6679b506092e7b244d74aad25083c019280d423","tid":1325351,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"又屈連登，幫bk 同香討食死猫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b529d08d8287df3c47edb6b197ec598b53e750","tid":1325351,"uid":245998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"連你老母<br />\n明明係discuss同uwants"},{"pid":"6906b2afa5cdb626769acdc308ef2cb391da4ccc","tid":1325351,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"痴撚線發夢姐<br />\n香討班人就真係堅喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac579e7cab3a376180c9adfb3e4f318817b00262","tid":1325351,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:01:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔都係個講字，我就唔信有咁大影響力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c12eead7649b89811533850cc6819378a34ee6","tid":1325351,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:30:46.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都知係bk, 香討同U汪班人做既<br />\n但請連登仔們不割𥱊不督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}